# Dapp H5 Guide

A step-by-step guide to accessing and using the LinkLayerAI DApp on mobile (H5).

### Step 1

Open the LinkLayerAI Dapp👉 (https://agent.linklayer.ai/)

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/2.png)

### Step 2

Click "Log in" in the top right corner and connect your wallet (Note: Use a wallet address that holds Binance Alpha tokens)

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/3.png)

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/4.png)

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/5.png)

### Step 3

After logging in, click your account address in the top right corner to view account information: wallet address, bound email, point balance, and referral count.

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/6.png)

Click the point button in the top right corner to enter the Points Recharge interface.

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/7.png)

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/8.png)

Click "Earn" in the top right corner to copy your referral link with one click, or share directly via Twitter for promotion.

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/9.png)

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/10.png)

### Step 4

Alpha Agent: Click "Alpha" on the left to view all Binance Alpha token holdings for the current address. The traffic light indicates each token's liquidity health: Green = sufficient liquidity, Red = liquidity depletion risk, Yellow = transitional state.

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/11.png)

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/12.png)

Click "Explorer" to jump directly to the token's block explorer page. Click "Agent" to analyze the token's liquidity status.

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/13.png)

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/14.png)

### Step 5

Click "Insight" on the left, click "+", select "Binance", fill in your Binance read-only API Key and Secret Key, and confirm.

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/15.png)

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/16.png)

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/17.png)

After successfully binding the Binance read-only API, the Binance icon will light up.

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/18.png)

The black box below displays your exchange spot holdings list. Click on any token icon and the Agent will provide real-time analysis and suggestions.

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/19.png)

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/20.png)

Perps Mining：  
Retroactive：A one-time reward issued after you connect your API, automatically calculated based on your liquidation history from the past 6 months.  
Recurring：Ongoing rewards distributed every 30 days, based on your new liquidation records during each period.

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/21.png)

Perps Pilot: Click on your current perpetual positions in the exchange. The Agent will provide real-time analysis and recommendations for your perpetual positions.

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/22.png)

### Step 6

Click "Piloter" on the left. Select any token in "Picker" and the Agent can provide real-time analysis for spot or perpetual.

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/23.png)

Enter the token name you want to analyze in the search box.

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/24.png)

Click the ⭐️ in front of tokens you're interested in to pin them.

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/25.png)

In "Tracker", tokens matching specific strategies will be filtered and displayed based on your selected strategy.

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/26.png)

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/26-1.png)

### Step 7

Click "Graph" on the left to view your referral graph.

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/27.png)

### Step 8

Click "Rewards" on the left to swap LLA for LLAX and stake your tokens.

![](https://cdn.linklayer.ai/uploads/dapph5guide/28.png)
